{"tid":1544231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際反華戰線】煲底一句葡文噴漆connect埋巴西人！","createTime":"2019-09-05T13:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T19:00:10.000Z","uid":108502,"like":309,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6499e006fafc4a7883681de0d68b2c254ad3c1","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=522324e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&h=e399dacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg%3Alarge&h=2abf9297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有位手足喺煲底寫咗巴西獨立革命嘅格言：Independ&ecirc;ncia ou Morte （不獨立毋寧死）<br />\n而且仲要撞正巴西獨立日  (9月7號)<br />\n令到好多巴西人好感動！位手足真係好有sense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗國際反華戰線 大家第日做民宣都可以用多啲各國語言 引用下外國革命嘅事蹟 connect世界各地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為我哋嘅10月1號全球反華大遊行造勢！"},{"pid":"1612fca014f71658556ff4635c333994f844f5d5","tid":1544231,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"176a7f54b244106a2a3f84c58a9a4bd6a6dea77b","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"以下用少量葡文知識譯下留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLORwpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLORwpK.jpg&h=13e37e09&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（前略）求主垂憐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0fwwrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0fwwrn.jpg&h=bb5397fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n&gt;&gt;香港以前係英國嘅殖民地 但我估係一個移民咗去香港嘅澳門人寫?<br />\n&gt;&gt;都make sense嘅 不過我唔覺囉哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係咪澳門巴打寫嘅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhsiVTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhsiVTU.jpg&h=23c74b02&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港人對抗中共政府爭取自由，而我哋嘅國父D. Pedro係佢哋嘅啟發；而喺巴西，有人鄙視我哋嘅英雄，仲話巴西需要一個共產政府！但巴西永遠唔會赤化！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ugS0nf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ugS0nf.jpg&h=a0a58f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(引用巴西獨立頌)     為我們鍛造的枷鎖    奸詐狡猾的詭計    有一雙最強有力的手    笑對它們，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span></ins> <br />\nretweet回應: 香港人已經展視出佢哋會為獨立而戰到最後一刻！我睇下中國敢唔敢鎮壓佢哋！<br />\n(希望無譯錯 但依度真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外都有好多retweet係po返巴西獨立頌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0Y2DaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0Y2DaG.jpg&h=ea0ca4e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n依句說話係Dom Pedro爭取獨立嘅宣言；希望你哋都做得到！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A49YbxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA49YbxN.jpg&h=66c5af8d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 香港人講依句嘢真係好啱 因為佢哋嘅目標就係同當年嘅巴西一樣 成為英國事實上嘅殖民地 俾債務同埋不平等貿易整死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 依條友為專制主義鼓掌 而認為貿易會為人帶來奴役<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6b97ef1891be6fe87fbcc626ccbeb93e62105d","tid":1544231,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145973e5e63b83c1871a55efa402a8c076938ee6","tid":1544231,"uid":158045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"20b7458fa2487fbe1b0bbf0ac338c2ceaf2cbb97","tid":1544231,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7000724384b465bbe6ed70ddac0536fc88f85b16","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"推爆佢！"},{"pid":"fbc48567e8160017cd5abbe5ab8cf3e1a2e693e7","tid":1544231,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"3f23755d6af2a1ad4d1381699ba82a70666e861b","tid":1544231,"uid":202340,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"澳門狗又喺度說三道四"},{"pid":"1d43a2569dc86f6535beb5a7852941c5aae89b10","tid":1544231,"uid":28202,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1a6499e006fafc4a7883681de0d68b2c254ad3c1","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=522324e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&h=e399dacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDn-HpOUUA