3dada02b55c236654a42fd42437398cfc131b6","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5995fbff30fd36872698e2f5b26cbd762cc8892","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4c967d575de8a27d3345dedf3bc7b18301fc3f","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3edb5e8878b5a907f49e6514858ae82df833db9","tid":1544231,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"f0db7d4bbe2c79461cd649ad6eb8da38efa9bbbc","tid":1544231,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people. <br />\nNo one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><del>WINTER ON FIRE</del><br />\n《HONG KONG BE WATER》</strong></span></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">港共企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵站傷亡</span>、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺事件、<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻止民主人權法案</span></strong></span>、<br />\n模糊 臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">清朝債主權問題</span></span>等<br />\n</strong>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span>事件焦點<br />\n</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美、德 領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n國際審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 <br />\n還原港人高度自治 落實港人雙普選 <br />\n協助<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重新制定</span></span>民主進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 <strong>高壓滅聲</strong> 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">港府管治班子自治權名存實亡</span>  聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐嚇 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n重申 <strong><ins>五大政諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面落實</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: green;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n華夏遺珠 高度自治</span> </em></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">人權民主法案</span> 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n破而後立<br />\n國際自由港🕊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">這不單是 反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>流水革命 元年</div></ins></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b63964442d6d8ffef63712151b954d4a7a810492","tid":1544231,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"9.06 7:30pm 遮打 反濫暴<br />\n9.07 1:00pm 機場見<br />\n9.08 2:00pm 美國駐港澳領事館"},{"pid":"2313a47c8c862a2521c5b8c6cba167dfb3e60dab","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi