l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIndepend&ecirc;ncia ou Morte 就係佢嘅格言<br />\n而巴西獨立頌亦係由佢所作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb2b9fda597451a8cedabd7751848ec818541a","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447537df8e9af428b523f3f0efb4395d5083ae3a","tid":1544231,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fb9cd33545702d6c3d325cf84290330ac8d64d5","tid":1544231,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"馬交人識唔識睇？"},{"pid":"623e63a320cff36863a22ff19d96917fe0a1a633","tid":1544231,"uid":239035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"59290a54bc08367b53f68ef2f0dedd358371c5a6","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531e5725fff8a722204280fbd71a3accceeb05d6","tid":1544231,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5109a3094276ec0b4f4ee246b17e2ca43f81e6c0","tid":1544231,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"